WEBVTT


00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:04.200
2024 is gonna be one of the great political years.

00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:05.800
If you like elections.

00:00:05.800 --> 00:00:07.380
There's 40 of them.

00:00:07.400 --> 00:00:10.200
Eight are critical in critical countries,

00:00:10.200 --> 00:00:11.360
from Taiwan,

00:00:11.360 --> 00:00:12.400
through South Africa

00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:15.920
to Russia to the United States of America.

00:00:15.920 --> 00:00:18.840
And it's all taking place in an environment which is

00:00:18.840 --> 00:00:19.800
geopolitically,

00:00:19.800 --> 00:00:23.600
deeply unstable and economically very depressed.

00:00:23.600 --> 00:00:24.600
So, therefore,

00:00:24.600 --> 00:00:27.960
predicting those elections in 2024 is gonna be very,

00:00:27.960 --> 00:00:29.980
very difficult indeed.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:31.500
Watch this space.
